      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COUSIN SAL (5) had won two starts on end leading into the last outing when strongly fancied but could only manage fifth (29.99) at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Can bounce back. BLAZING WARRIOR (8) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his flying 22.77 win at this track over 400m. Must include on winning run two back. ZIPPING PFEIFFER (4) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 2.75 lengths (29.76) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Rates a leading chance again. FASCINATE JOHN (2) is right in the mix.",
